snippet.textDisplay:
This game easily has the most epic and dramatic Master Sword scene of all the Zelda games. With each of the games it's a big thing yeah, but here, you only mess with the sword once to make it seem that much more grand, not to mention you're so happy it's not a fake! The fog, the animals, and then...your pearls rise-they shine and Link goes to pull. The fog clears, a ray of light shines down upon Link from between the trees, he pulls up the sword! It glimmers with the light to banish evil!
Epic.
snippet.textOriginal:
This game easily has the most epic and dramatic Master Sword scene of all the Zelda games. With each of the games it's a big thing yeah, but here, you only mess with the sword once to make it seem that much more grand, not to mention you're so happy it's not a fake! The fog, the animals, and then...your pearls rise-they shine and Link goes to pull. The fog clears, a ray of light shines down upon Link from between the trees, he pulls up the sword! It glimmers with the light to banish evil!
Epic.
